high_descs: Turn around and head to the room across the passage to reach the diningtable.
Pick up the yellow knife from the round table.
Turn around and head left to reach the kitchen on the left to reach the tomato in the fridge.
Cut the tomato with the knife in the fridge.
Turn right to reach the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the fridge.
Turn right to reach the microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave.
Turn around to head out of the kitchen and turn right to head down the passage and turn left to reach the desk on the right in the bedroom.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Turn right to head out of the room and turn right to head down the passage and turn left to reach the microwave in the kitchen.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
Take out the knife from the microwave.
Close the microwave door with the tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Put the tomato in the microwave and shut the door.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Take the knife from the table.
Turn around and go near the tomato.
Cut the tomato into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the knife into the microwave.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take the tomato from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the tomato into the microwave.
Turn around and go to the desk in the bedroom.
Take the tomato from the table.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the tomato into the microwave.
Then take the knife from the oven.
Cut the tomato into pieces using the knife.
anns.task_desc: Cut the tomato into the pieces using the knife.

high_descs: Turn around, take a step forward, then go right into a corridor, immediately take an exit on the left, and walk up to a round diningtable in the opposite corner.
Pick up the knife from the round table.
Leave the room, go back where you started, and head left to a tomato fridge.
Cut the tomato with the knife inside the fridge.
Go to the microwave in the right corner beside the fridge.
Put the knife inside the microwave.
Go back to the fridge.
Take a tomato slice out of the fridge.
Move back to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice inside the microwave.
Head back to the corridor, continue straight until an entrance in the upper left, and go to the distant side of a desk.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Get back to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
Take the knife out of the microwave.
Cut the tomato with the knife in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Have a whole tomato cut and a tomato slice in the microwave.
